<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/92d7e21697c143b68f8bed90baa8ce65.jpeg" /></p>
<p><strong><span>美在雪乡</span></strong></p>
<p><span>雪乡，美到用语言无法形容</span></p>
<p><span>白天，就像是一幅水墨画</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/bc52919472d946c49fc13c728ff39654.png" /></p>
<p><span>夜晚，更有一番韵味</span></p>
<p><span>白雪在大红灯笼的照射下</span></p>
<p><span>显得那样的温暖</span></p>
<p><span>犹如迈进</span><strong><span>童话世界的雪堡</span></strong></p>
<p><span>如果恰巧你喜欢拍照</span></p>
<p><span>那么</span></p>
<p><span>雪乡里有各种款式的</span><strong><span>民族服饰</span></strong></p>
<p><span>供你选择</span></p>
<p><span>任性留念</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/fcf2373aa5f14c518f5aad63eb1e53ac.png" /></p>
<p><span>唯美的</span></p>
<p><span>硬朗的</span></p>
<p><span>霸气的</span></p>
<p><span>......</span></p>
<p><span>这些美好回忆值得</span><strong><span>永久珍存</span></strong></p>
