<p><strong><span>玩在雪乡</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>在这里</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>你可以</span><strong><span>滑雪圈</span></strong><span>、坐</span><strong><span>冰上碰碰车</span></strong><span>、</span><strong><span>滑雪</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>您还可以乘坐</span><strong><span>雪地摩托</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>感受风驰电掣的速度与激情</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>乘坐</span><strong><span>马拉爬犁</span></strong><span>畅游林海雪原</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>体验</span><strong><span>狗拉爬犁</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>与皑皑白雪来一次最亲密的接触</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/b041730d21e34875b98c54a5972bb465.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>棒槌山山寨</span></p>
<p><span>雪乡文化展览馆</span></p>
<p><span>东北大秧歌表演等</span></p>
<p><span>诸多免费景点等你来玩</span></p>
<p><span>雪乡 </span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span>东北</span></strong></p>
