<p><span>到位于雪乡西北角的</span><strong><span>羊草山</span></strong></p>
<p><span>看日出</span></p>
<p><span>亲手敲响</span><strong><span>“太阳神鼓”</span></strong></p>
<p><span>祈福诸事顺利，福星高照</span></p>
