<p><strong><span>乐在雪乡</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>本次</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>“最北龙江飘雪时”</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>点燃了2020 <span>年雪乡的</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>第一把火</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>为全网的宝贝们</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>贡献了今年雪乡的</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">篝火首秀</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>2020雪乡篝火首秀</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/d4ccc6f6884444bb889f55051c80c660.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>快看！</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>围着</span><strong><span>热情的篝火</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>现场伙伴们的激情也被点燃</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>他们</span><strong><span>尽情地唱跳</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>每个人脸上都洋溢着灿烂的微笑</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/aa97569eae55445c9afb8ab0fc7941b9.jpeg" /></p>
