<p><span>你看！</span></p>
<p><span>这展晨是</span><span><strong>“吃着碗里望着锅里的”</strong></span></p>
<p><span>这边放不下</span></p>
<p><span>特色的</span><strong><span>东北农家菜</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201114/d1f58bca8a054b6d82d1f23bd97f2dbf.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>又开始惦记那边的</span></p>
<p><span><strong>小烧烤、小火锅</strong></span></p>
<p><span>这馋得直咽口水</span></p>
